							<h1 class="video__title">
								<span data-syndicatable-target></span>
								<span data-syndicatable-title>The carbon capture question | FT Climate Capital</span>
							</h1>
							<p class="video__standfirst">Oil, gas and heavy industries such as cement and steel making are banking on developing systems that will deal with the emissions responsible for global warming. But the question of whether it can be done at the necessary scale and cost remains</p>
